      <title>奥尔班要求乌克兰与俄罗斯续签天然气协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-24/orban-links-eu-russia-sanctions-renewal-to-ukraine-gas-transit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[匈牙利总理维克托·奥尔班呼吁欧盟向乌克兰施压，要求其重新建立俄罗斯天然气向欧洲的输送通道，并将这一问题与延长对莫斯科的制裁联系起来。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-24/orban-links-eu-russia-sanctions-renewal-to-ukraine-gas-transit</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 07:32:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>富士电视台性丑闻引发政府对公众信任度的担忧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-24/fuji-media-shares-rebound-on-plan-to-form-investigation-panel</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本内阁大臣周五表示，富士媒体控股公司性骚扰丑闻可能会损害日本公众对广播的信任，该公司正努力控制这一问题，该丑闻已导致其股价动荡，并迫使日本一位顶级电视主持人宣布退出娱乐业。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-24/fuji-media-shares-rebound-on-plan-to-form-investigation-panel</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 02:04:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
